---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Technical SEO Services In The Philippines - Bright Forge SEO" description="Expert technical SEO services that optimize your website's foundation for maximum visibility and performance. Specialized technical solutions for Philippine businesses.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-content">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
      <nav class="breadcrumbs">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="separator">›</span>
        <span class="current">Technical SEO Services Philippines</span>
      </nav>
      
      <div class="hero-content-text">
        <h1>Technical SEO Services In The Philippines</h1>
        <div class="hero-story">
          <p>Have you ever wondered why your website isn't performing as well as it should, despite having great content and beautiful design? I've seen it countless times—business owners investing heavily in their online presence only to be held back by invisible technical barriers. One client came to us after spending months creating premium content that simply wasn't ranking. The culprit? Technical SEO issues that were hiding their site from Google's view.</p>
          
          <p>At Bright Forge SEO, we specialize in uncovering and fixing these hidden obstacles. Our technical SEO services go beyond surface-level optimizations to address the foundational elements that search engines care about most. We transform your website into a well-oiled machine that both search engines and users love to interact with—because when your technical foundation is solid, everything else falls into place.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Fix Your Technical Foundation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Technical SEO Section -->
  <section class="why-technical-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Technical SEO Is Your Website's <span>Secret Weapon</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-explanation">
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="content-text">
            <p>Technical SEO is like the engine of your car—you don't see it, but it powers everything. While content and backlinks get most of the attention, technical issues can completely undermine your SEO efforts if left unaddressed. Search engines need to efficiently crawl, render, and index your website before your content even has a chance to rank.</p>
            
            <p>Our technical SEO services ensure your website meets and exceeds Google's increasingly demanding technical requirements, giving you a competitive edge in the Philippine market where many businesses still overlook these critical optimizations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Technical SEO Services Section -->
  <section class="services-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Core Technical SEO <span>Services</span></h2>
        <p>We dive deep into your website's architecture to optimize every technical aspect that impacts your search performance.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-sitemap"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Site Architecture Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>URL structure optimization</li>
            <li>Internal linking analysis and improvement</li>
            <li>Site hierarchy restructuring</li>
            <li>XML sitemap optimization</li>
            <li>robots.txt configuration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Performance Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Page speed optimization</li>
            <li>Core Web Vitals improvement</li>
            <li>Server response time optimization</li>
            <li>Resource minification and compression</li>
            <li>Image optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Mobile Optimization</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Mobile-first indexing compliance</li>
            <li>Responsive design verification</li>
            <li>Mobile usability fixes</li>
            <li>Touch element spacing</li>
            <li>Mobile page speed optimization</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Security & Indexing</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>SSL implementation</li>
            <li>HTTPS migration</li>
            <li>Security header configuration</li>
            <li>Crawl optimization</li>
            <li>Index coverage improvement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process Section -->
  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Technical SEO <span>Process</span></h2>
        <p>We follow a systematic approach to identify, fix, and monitor your website's technical health.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Technical Audit</h3>
            <p>We perform a comprehensive technical analysis of your website using advanced tools to identify all issues affecting your search performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Issue Prioritization</h3>
            <p>We categorize and prioritize technical issues based on their impact on your search rankings and user experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Implementation Plan</h3>
            <p>We create a detailed roadmap for fixing technical issues, ensuring changes are made safely and effectively.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Optimization Execution</h3>
            <p>Our team implements the necessary technical fixes and optimizations, carefully monitoring for any potential impacts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Testing & Validation</h3>
            <p>We thoroughly test all changes across different devices and browsers to ensure everything works perfectly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">6</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Monitoring & Maintenance</h3>
            <p>We continuously monitor your website's technical health and performance, addressing new issues as they arise.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Benefits of Strong <span>Technical SEO</span></h2>
        <p>Investing in technical SEO delivers lasting advantages for your website and business.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Improved Rankings</h3>
          <p>A technically optimized website has a better chance of ranking higher in search results, as search engines can easily crawl and understand your content.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Faster Loading Times</h3>
          <p>Technical optimizations lead to faster page loading times, reducing bounce rates and improving user engagement.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Better User Experience</h3>
          <p>A well-structured, fast-loading website provides a superior user experience, leading to higher conversion rates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Mobile Excellence</h3>
          <p>Your website will perform flawlessly across all devices, capturing the growing mobile audience in the Philippines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <ContactSection />

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
/* Existing styles remain... */

/* Services Section */
.services-section {
  padding: 80px 0;
  background: #f8f9fa;
}

.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 30px;
  margin-top: 50px;
}

.service-card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 30px;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.service-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.service-icon {
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF4438, #FF6B5B);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.service-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.service-card ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.service-card ul li {
  padding: 8px 0;
  color: #666;
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 25px;
}

.service-card ul li:before {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: #FF4438;
  font-weight: bold;
}

/* Process Section */
.process-section {
  padding: 80px 0;
  background: white;
}

.process-steps {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 30px;
  margin-top: 50px;
}

.step-card {
  background: #f8f9fa;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 30px;
  position: relative;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.step-number {
  position: absolute;
  top: -20px;
  left: 30px;
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF4438, #FF6B5B);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  color: white;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.step-content {
  margin-top: 15px;
}

.step-content h3 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.step-content p {
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Benefits Section */
.benefits-section {
  padding: 80px 0;
  background: #f8f9fa;
}

.benefits-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 30px;
  margin-top: 50px;
}

.benefit-card {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 30px;
  text-align: center;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.benefit-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
}

.benefit-icon {
  width: 70px;
  height: 70px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF4438, #FF6B5B);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 20px;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
}

.benefit-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.benefit-card p {
  color: #666;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .services-grid,
  .process-steps,
  .benefits-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .step-card {
    padding-top: 40px;
  }

  .service-card,
  .benefit-card {
    padding: 20px;
  }
}
</style>

<style>
/* Hero Section */
.hero-content {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
  padding: 60px 0 80px;
  position: relative;
}

.breadcrumbs {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  font-size: 14px;
}

.breadcrumbs a {
  color: #666;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.breadcrumbs a:hover {
  color: #FF4438;
}

.separator {
  margin: 0 10px;
  color: #999;
}

.current {
  color: #FF4438;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.hero-content-text {
  max-width: 800px;
}

.hero-content-text h1 {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.hero-story {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.hero-story p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.cta-button {
  display: inline-block;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF4438, #FF6B5B);
  color: white;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 15px 30px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(255, 68, 56, 0.2);
}

.cta-button:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(255, 68, 56, 0.3);
}

/* Why Technical SEO Section */
.why-technical-section {
  padding: 80px 0;
  background: #fff;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.section-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  line-height: 1.3;
}

.section-header h2 span {
  color: #FF4438;
}

.content-explanation {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}

.content-card {
  display: flex;
  max-width: 900px;
  background: #f8f9fa;
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.content-icon {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 100px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF4438, #FF6B5B);
  color: white;
  font-size: 2rem;
}

.content-text {
  padding: 30px;
}

.content-text p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero-content-text h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
  
  .content-card {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .content-icon {
    width: 100%;
    height: 80px;
  }
}
</style>
